Wolverine  The Road to Hell # 1 [CBR]


Wolverine starts down the road to hell and we want to take you along for the ride?it all starts here! With all new material by the creative teams bringing you WOLVERINE, X-23, DAKEN: DARK WOLVERINE and X-FORCE, The Road to Hell is packed with clues and signposts to help you find your way through the brand-new launch of Wolverine?s own family of books! You won?t want to miss it, because bonus material includes a second look at the first issue of Namor the First Mutant #1 and an exclusive preview of the November launch of an ALL NEW X-BOOK! You won?t want to miss it!
